def export_users_to_xlsx(filename):
    workbook = openpyxl.Workbook()
    sheet = workbook.active
    sheet.title = 'Users'
    sheet.append(['Telegram ID', ' ', ''])
    users = User.objects.all()
    for user in users:
        sheet.append([user.tg_id, user.tg_username, user.name])
    workbook.save(filename)
